158    public QuickBolusIncrement getQuickBolusIncrement() {
159        if (!isQuickBolusEnabled()) {
160            return QuickBolusIncrement.DISABLED;
161        }
162
163        // units
164        if (getQuickBolusEntryType() == 0) {
165            switch (getQuickBolusIncrementUnits()) {
166                case 500:
167                    return QuickBolusIncrement.UNITS_0_5;
168                case 1000:
169                    return QuickBolusIncrement.UNITS_1_0;
170                case 2000:
171                    return QuickBolusIncrement.UNITS_2_0;
172                case 5000:
173                    return QuickBolusIncrement.UNITS_5_0;
174            }
175        } else if (getQuickBolusEntryType() == 1) {
176            switch (getQuickBolusIncrementCarbs()) {
177                case 2000:
178                    return QuickBolusIncrement.CARBS_2G;
179                case 5000:
180                    return QuickBolusIncrement.CARBS_5G;
181                case 10000:
182                    return QuickBolusIncrement.CARBS_10G;
183                case 15000:
184                    return QuickBolusIncrement.CARBS_15G;
185            }
186        }
187        return null;
188    }
